user: I think I'll stop here and ask about the transportation options from EWR to Manhattan. How do the train and bus services from EWR to Manhattan compare in terms of cost, convenience, and travel time?
assistant: The transportation options from EWR to Manhattan are a crucial part of your travel experience.

